node.text:
Sports has always played a big role and it teached me a lot in life. I'm honoured to work with @laureussport foundation to give my experiences and everything sports teached me to other people. We want to help especially children who are not priviledged to be able to get active and show them what sports can give them. I'm really excited to work on this project and give everyone a chance to feel the joy of sports 🙏🏼

Felt great to spend this awesome day together with  @svenkueenle @benemayr @eliaselhardt who also joined forces with Laureus 👍

🔥 GIVEAWAY 🔥
Update: winner - @zezinho_pereira - Congrats 🙏🏼

with unique parts of mine. 
All you need to do to enter: 
1. Follow @nineyard_ and @canyon_cllctv 
2. Tag 2 buddies in the comments you ride your playgrounds with. 
3. Add #CreatePlaygrounds before posting your comment

The winner will be announced on the Nineyard website on 09 07 21! 
Let's go wild 🤘🏼
